./qooxdoo-2.0.2-sdk/tool/bin/create-application.py --name qxtest3

Change to the new directory:
cd qxtest3

Generate:
./generate.py source-all

Navigate (with IE) to the new app:
http://localhost/qxtest3/source
-&gt; the page is blank

